Package io.github.waileong.fcm.service.domain

Class FcmMessage

java.lang.Object
io.github.waileong.fcm.service.domain.FcmMessage
public class FcmMessage extends Object
Represents a Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) message that can be sent to a client app. This class encapsulates various FCM message options such as data payload, notification details, and platform-specific configurations (Android, Webpush, APNs).

Instances of this class can be constructed using the nested FcmMessage.Builder class.

For more details on Android message configuration, refer to the Firebase documentation: Message
